metadata.name: Sea Friend #1
metadata.description: Sea Friends is a community curated collectibles project featuring 1000 exclusive creatures that have recently surfaced from the ocean and made their way onto land to join the Metaverse. Much like humans, no two Sea Friends are alike, all unique in their own way. Your Sea Friends doubles as your $eaweed membership card, and grants access to members-only benefits like SF airdrops, raffles, community giveaways, and more fun events. Each unique Sea Friends digital collectible comes in a joyful range of styles, colors and traits. Some rarer than others, but all aesthetically vibing for a good time. Visit [seafriends.io](https://seafriends.io) for more details.
